The results of the material validation assessment by material experts for content and purpose variables, material presentation, tests, and efficiency have shown the criteria of "Very Valid". C. Practicality Test Results
Table 3. Practicality Test Result Variable % Usage 4,78 Benefits 4,69 Display and Language 4,70 Material Presentation 4,75 Rata-rata 4,73 The results of the practicality test conducted by 16 grade VII students of SMP Pertiwi 2 Padang with these results are included in the criteria of "Very Practical".
4. CONCLUSION
Based on the results of the validity test conducted by two media experts and one material expert with “very valid” validity results and the practicality test conducted by 16 grade VII students of SMP Pertiwi 2 Padang with the results of the practicality test is “very practical”. So it can be concluded that interactive multimedia using the smart apps creator application in class VII Junior High School Informatics subjects that have been developed is “very valid” and “very practical”. Then interactive multimedia is worth using in the learning process.
